Survived: Passenger Survival ( 0 = No, 1 = Yes )

Sex: Passenger Sex

Age: Passenger Age

Pclass: Passenger Class ( 1 = first, 2 = second, 3 = third )

SibSp: Number of Siblings/Spouses Aboard

Parch: Number of Parents/Children Aboard

Fare: Ticket Fare

Embarked: Port of Embarkation ( C = Cherbourg, Q = Queenstown, S = Southampton )

Title: Passenger Title: Mrs ( includes Mrs, Mme, Lady, Mlle, Ms), Mr (includes Mr, Sir, Dr), Major (includes Major, Capt, Don, Col, Jonkheer, Master), Miss (includes Miss, Dona, the Countess, Rev, Mlle)

FamilySize ( = SibSp + Parch + 1): Number of Family Members

CabinPr: Cabin Presence ( 0 = No, 1 = Yes )
